title: Vaccination Research: Mom Shares Vaccine Horrors And Won’t Vaccinate
description:
http://www.StopMandatoryVaccination.com - After doing her research, this mom discovered that vaccines can cause great harm, including death, and that natural immunity is superior to vaccination. She never vaccinated her 4 year-old daughter, who shines with vibrant health. A few things she discovered during her massive research process: 
• The risk of vaccines are higher than the chances of her daughter getting Whooping Cough
• Polio is not a threat to our society, except from vaccination
• Vaccine makers cannot be sued for injury or death
• Vaccines have toxic ingredients
• Vaccines have Thimerosal in them, a dangerous mercury “preservative”
• Thimerosal increased in utero once flu shots started to be pushed onto pregnant women
• Injection is different than ingestion: for example, you can drink snake venom and not die, but get bit by a snake, and that can kill you
• Over 3 billion dollars has been paid out for vaccine related injury and vaccine related death
• Vaccines are not safe
• Why is our infant mortality rate so high and also the highest vaccination rate? Could it be the vaccines?
• Every parent deserves to know the full Truth about the dangers of vaccination before vaccinating their child. Learn more here:
• http://www.stopmandatoryvaccination.com/personal-choice/

Stop Mandatory Vaccination

Founder and Director of http://www.StopMandatoryVaccination.com
